{"tid":1355750,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【終年90歲】六四「屠夫」李鵬去世 89年宣佈戒嚴上演血腥鎮壓","createTime":"2019-07-23T11:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T11:35:41.000Z","uid":174351,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c2db58be66c0e1df014ecaffe000731c05d13c4d","tid":1355750,"uid":174351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:06:08.000Z","msg":"新華社報道，國務院前總理李鵬於7月22日去世，終年90歲。<br />\n<br />\n新華社通報，中國共產黨中央委員會、中華人民共和國全國人民代表大會常務委員會、中華人民共和國國務院、中國人民政治協商會議全國委員會沉痛宣告：中國共產黨的優秀黨員，久經考驗的忠誠的共產主義戰士，傑出的無產階級革命家、政治家，黨和國家的卓越領導人，中國共產黨第十二屆中央政治局委員、中央書記處書記，第十三屆、十四屆、十五屆中央政治局常委，國務院原總理，第九屆全國人民代表大會常務委員會委員長李鵬同志，因病醫治無效，於2019年7月22日晚上11時11分在北京逝世。<br />\n<br />\n終於落地府了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ce1096f65730d5f08096e2b3c4b143585bcd912","tid":1355750,"uid":204976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:06:34.000Z","msg":"今日實在太高興啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128459a8165dae71809bf37c99272fd74fe817b5","tid":1355750,"uid":174752,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:07:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zm9iYR6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZm9iYR6.jpg&h=1143255e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9f0c5340aad63f8974058e721359768bc8e45bd1","tid":1355750,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:08:00.000Z","msg":"吊左幾耐命"},{"pid":"d3ea8a1cdb44a245d9f970e62ae8476f0c58408f","tid":1355750,"uid":252085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:08:23.000Z","msg":"今日發生嘅開心事係對我哋一個好大嘅鼓舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab8570f058dc2656ebbc8b899b66bb9e7291880","tid":1355750,"uid":187232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EEFexkY.png\"